Class ExerciseRange

java.lang.Object
com.fitnessforge.utils.ExerciseRange
public class ExerciseRange extends Object
Description:

An Helper class for WorkoutService which helps in algorithm of exercise selection, providing the necessary details of exercise like reps, sets and duration.
